data.description: Punta Gorda waterfront. This 3 bedroom 2 bath 2 car garage on an oversized corner lot is a diamond in the rough. The home is in good shape with a new roof in the last year. It can use some fresh paint and carpet. This home sits in the heart of Punta Gorda and is close to downtown and shopping. The home offers Dock, Large Lanai as well as an outside deck overlooking the canal. This is what you come to Florida for and is a must-see.
